'''Abel Quiller''' was an alias used on occasion by [[Talon Karrde]]. [[Dankin]] often acted as Quiller so as to keep Karrde from being recognized. Quiller was supposedly the impatient captain of the ''[[Wild Karrde|Hab Camber]]''.

